OL,3,CNottingham Forest fined #750,000 for
OL,4,Csocial media posts about match
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,FNottingham Forest have been fined
OL,8,F#750,000 by the Football Association
OL,9,Ffor social media posts they made about
OL,10,Fmatch officials.
OL,12,FThe club took to X to complain about
OL,13,Fthree penalty decisions that weren't
OL,14,Fawarded in a 2-0 defeat to Everton in
OL,15,FApril.
OL,17,FThe result had left Forest one point
OL,18,Fabove the relegation zone.
