OL,7,FAt the time Nottingham Forest said in
OL,8,Fthe post "Three extremely poor
OL,9,Fdecisions - three penalties not given
OL,10,F- which we simply cannot accept.
OL,12,F"We warned the PGMOL that the VAR is a
OL,13,FLuton fan before the game but they
OL,14,Fdidn't change him.
OL,16,F"Our patience has been tested multiple
OL,17,Ftimes. NFFC will now consider its
OL,18,Foptions."
OL,20,FIn a statement today the club said:
