OL,3,CNottingham Forest fined #750,000 for
OL,4,Csocial media posts about match
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,F"Nottingham Forest Football Club is
OL,8,Fextremely disappointed with the
OL,9,Fdecision of the Regulatory Commission
OL,10,Fto impose a #750,000 fine in relation
OL,11,Fto comments posted on social media
OL,12,Ffollowing our Premier League fixture
OL,13,Fagainst Everton on Sunday 21 April.
OL,15,FWe are particularly concerned that The
OL,16,FFA, in its submissions, sought a
OL,17,Fsanction "in excess of #1,000,000".
