OL,3,CNottingham Forest fined #750,000 for
OL,4,Csocial media posts about match
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,F"We believe that this request, along
OL,8,Fwith the subsequent fine, is wholly
OL,9,Fdisproportionate and the Club will be
OL,10,Fappealing the decision".
OL,12,FThe FA's submission was that the fine
OL,13,Fshould be over, or at least equal to a
OL,14,Fmillion pounds, given that it in its
OL,15,Fview it attacked the integrity of an
OL,16,Fofficial and the game of football as a
OL,17,Fwhole "on an unparalleled scale".
OL,19,FThe Premier League issued their own
OL,20,Fstatement on social media saying:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
