OL,3,CNottingham Forest fined #750,000 for
OL,4,Csocial media posts about match
OL,5,Cofficials
OL,7,F"The Premier League was extremely
OL,8,Fdisappointed to read the comments made
OL,9,Fby Nottingham Forest on social media
OL,10,Fyesterday, following its match against
OL,11,FEverton.
OL,13,F"We note The FA has confirmed it will
OL,14,Fbe investigating the club's statement.
OL,16,F"It is never appropriate to improperly
OL,17,Fquestion the integrity of match
OL,18,Fofficials, and the nature of these
OL,19,Fcomments means the Premier League will
OL,20,Falso be investigating the matter in
OL,21,Frelation to the League's Rules."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
